every minute of every day.

977
00:54:15.464 --> 00:54:21.470
Like a dark storm of. like. regret
and self-loathing. and I hate myself.

978
00:54:24.473 --> 00:54:29.602
I hate myself.
and I hate so much that I hurt you. Mel.

979
00:54:29.603 --> 00:54:31.355
You have no idea.

980
00:54:34.358 --> 00:54:35.817
[Samantha breathes shakily]

981
00:54:39.321 --> 00:54:40.322
Okay.

982
00:54:43.909 --> 00:54:45.577
And now I'll go.

983
00:54:47.037 --> 00:54:48.038
Wait.

984
00:54:53.877 --> 00:54:55.629
Sit here a minute.

985
00:55:02.970 --> 00:55:04.555
- I just--
- But don't talk.

986
00:55:15.148 --> 00:55:16.358
Chivo.

987
00:55:26.034 --> 00:55:27.035
[sighs]

988
00:55:36.378 --> 00:55:37.461
[sighs]

989
00:55:37.462 --> 00:55:38.713
[upbeat music playing]

990
00:55:38.714 --> 00:55:40.340
Got enough cheese there. Brad?

991
00:55:43.135 --> 00:55:45.721
- Yeah. this is good.
- [Peter] Oh. no. Fuck.

992
00:55:49.433 --> 00:55:51.017
Now. I want you to be honest. Tony.

993
00:55:51.018 --> 00:55:52.977
Would you ever hang
something like this in your own home?

994
00:55:52.978 --> 00:55:54.437
- Fuck. no.
- [chuckling]

995
00:55:54.438 --> 00:55:57.565
Coop. you've gotta stop Nick
from hanging this up.

996
00:55:57.566 --> 00:56:00.985
- Uh. I gotta take this. Sorry. guys.
- [phone buzzing]

997
00:56:00.986 --> 00:56:02.236
[Ashe] There he is!

998
00:56:02.237 --> 00:56:05.865
Coop. There's my badass motherfucker.

999
00:56:05.866 --> 00:56:07.700
- You did it.
- Okay?

1000
00:56:07.701 --> 00:56:09.243
Excelsior. you did it.

1001
00:56:09.244 --> 00:56:10.703
I didn't think
you'd be able to pull it off.

1002
00:56:10.704 --> 00:56:12.038
- No offense.
- None taken.

1003
00:56:12.039 --> 00:56:14.332
You are a fucking legend.
You know that? We're gonna celebrate.

1004
00:56:14.333 --> 00:56:16.667
We're gonna fucking party right now.
We're gonna celebrate. We're gonna party.

1005
00:56:16.668 --> 00:56:19.295
- Let's party. Let's go.
- You know. I just have to take this call.

1006
00:56:19.296 --> 00:56:21.215
Give me… Give me one second. Thanks.

1007
00:56:21.924 --> 00:56:23.467
Hey. yeah…

1008
00:56:26.136 --> 00:56:27.137
What?

1009
00:56:29.097 --> 00:56:30.265
No. uh…

1010
00:56:31.225 --> 00:56:33.976
No. no. no. you stay there.
I'll be there as soon as I can.

1011
00:56:33.977 --> 00:56:34.978
Yeah.

1012
00:56:36.730 --> 00:56:37.981
We good?

1013
00:56:40.400 --> 00:56:41.818
My dad just died.

